      public static User getByName(Hotel hotel, String name)
      Requests a user by their username
      Parameters:
      hotel - hotel of the user you want to request
      name - username of the User you want to request

      requested user (or null if user not found)

    • getByUniqueId

      public static User getByUniqueId(String uniqueId)
      Requests a user by their unique id
      Parameters:

      Returns:
      requested user (or null if user not found)
